\title{Group Query Attention}

\p{\em{Group query attention} is the same idea as [MQA](shazeerFastTransformerDecoding2019) but instead of using one #{K} and #{V} for every head, they use a \em{group} of them. Where obviously the number of groups needs to be less than the number of heads.}
